::DarkMouse::
She walks back to the comp and sits down infront of it.  She finds herself 
wondering when Scorponok will return.  She puts her feet up on the console 
and reclines in the chair a bit.  She places her hands behind her head and 
rests.
"Ah yes.  All in a days work. I wonder if Megatron would allow pink curtains 
in here?" She laughed out loud about that.
"Nah, blue maybe, but not pink."
She just chuckled and smiled to herself.  She was proud of the fact that she 
had found such a good base for her leaders to occupy.  She didn't care if 
she didn't get the credit for the find.  She was just pleased with herself 
for a job well done.
